on the first 13 q-coefficients, `ModularForm.eq_of_sturm_bound` lets us conclude that any
form with the same coefficients equals our explicit `lmfdb_1_148_a_orbit`.

Generated by `scripts/lmfdb_qexp_to_e4e6_v3.sage`.
